duties_responsibilities.duty: Develop relationships with members of the community to engage Medicare seniors with Oak Street Health.
Engage Medicare seniors with the goal of having those individuals become patients of Oak Street Health.
Work closely with Outreach Managers, Outreach Directors, and Community Relationship Managers to help drive new patient growth locally in their assigned territory.

education_certification.credential: Bachelor's degree in Sales, Marketing, or a related field (Master's preferred)
